 * - int _xtop = 5 : Top-level feature dimension
 * - double drop_out = 0.01 : Dropout rate
 *
 * Control Flags:
 * - bool is_mc = true : Monte Carlo data flag
 * - bool init = false : Initialization flag
 * - bool pagerank = false : Enable PageRank reconstruction
 *
 * RNN Networks:
 * - torch::nn::Sequential* rnn_x : Node encoding network
 * - torch::nn::Sequential* rnn_dx : Message passing network
