 * - torch::nn::Sequential* rnn_rxx : Resonance edge prediction  
 * - torch::nn::Sequential* rnn_hxx : Hidden state update
 *
 * MLP Networks:
 * - torch::nn::Sequential* mlp_ntop : Top multiplicity prediction
 * - torch::nn::Sequential* mlp_sig : Signal classification
 *
 * Null Buffers:
 * - torch::Tensor x_nulls : Node state buffer
 * - torch::Tensor dx_nulls : Edge state buffer
